<p><a href="#sdfootnote7anc" name="sdfootnote7sym">7</a><sup></sup>Simon demonstrates the possibility of mobilizing this kind of escape in his other works, which are based on the idea of an amateur production of knowledge and with subjects similar to that constructed by the artist in his <em>Homemade Electronic Watch</em>, as well as during a lecture given in Wolfsburg on <em>Edible Plants and Animals of Lower Saxony</em> or his <em>Sculptures from the Museum of a Man in Paris Recreated from the Drawings of Oskar Hansen and Lech Kunki and Printed on a Homemade 3d Printer.</em></p>
